name: Yumake L
text: This is a take and bake pizza place which they place all the ingredients on the pizza dough, then I take it home to bake it.   The food quality and service are great.   I  forgot to add pineapple in after the order was taken, but the gal was nice enough to make an exception and add it in at no extra charge.

name: Bobby Rauch
text: First I'd like to say we love the pizza. However since we moved to Lathrop a few months ago and have ordered pizza almost every week or every other week, that half the time we've ordered pizzas, there just isn't enough of the required â€¦More

name: Dennis Harrison
text: They were not going to take my coupon and there was no one in charge just some girl at the cash register and she refused to take my coupon so we left. Don't go there customer service is non-existent. Very bad customer service!

name: Brittany Thompson
text: Closed location!!! Why?! This was a go-to for us and it seemed busy. Disappointing :(

text: They're hella cheap on toppings they don't add enough at all
